      "comment": "CYCLONE SEBAS (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (23.66) in a Grade 4 at The Gardens. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Should be very hard to beat this time. ICE ON FIRE (4) was in winning form two back (23.27) at The Gardens but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. The form from his last run stacks up well. One of the better hopes. JET FUEL (3) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at The Gardens, scoring by a neck (15.91). Harder here but expected to feature again. MADE IN LONDON (8) has been in the money at her last two runs, most recently when third (17.53) in a Mix 1/2/3 over 300m at Taree Super Track.",
